{"tid":1505723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有冇手足係樂富九龍仔公園執到銀包","createTime":"2019-08-25T15:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:13:43.000Z","uid":188429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7444e367c6d8c1bd9ddad910689ce59f846c6f06","tid":1505723,"uid":188429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"代朋友出<br />\n<br />\n大約1900至1930左右。<br />\n岩岩去九龍仔公園向泳池方向行，跌左個銀包。<br />\n之後沿途有個姐姐，問我搵咩，佢話好似見到有人執左，行相反方向。<br />\n但我番轉頭搵已經冇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問球場職員都話冇人報失。<br />\n希望執到個位係巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑色Porter 入面信用卡，身份證都有<br />\n如果執到麻煩巴打聯絡我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntg：@Lucayeung1234<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aF62EPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaF62EPL.jpg&h=a6e5aff8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c54a7da7047bcd784bbe3fce2c0dc57ccd704ed","tid":1505723,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25aea4c121d467b878e11173cfac47a9631c1a0f","tid":1505723,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"何必帶咁多野呢？ 幫推"},{"pid":"66d3a65b8cba33aa66f1cb071b601b19ffda1dc7","tid":1505723,"uid":127309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">人人都係文宣！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位戰友，一齊加入Twitter戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"h